<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Cuenta creada — Sistema Universitario</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center p-6"
    style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d3f6e 0%, #1370a2 50%, #0f6e56 100%);">

    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 max-w-md w-full p-10 text-center">

        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
            </svg>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">¡Cuenta creada exitosamente!</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Bienvenido, <strong class="text-slate-700">{{name}}</strong>. Tu cuenta fue registrada sin problemas en el sistema universitario.
        </p>

        <a href="/dashboard"
           class="inline-block bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800 text-white text-sm font-medium px-7 py-2.5 rounded-lg transition-colors">
            Ir al Dashboard
        </a>

        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-5">Sistema Universitario · soporte@universidad.edu.ar</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>